BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF THE STATE OF HAWAII:
1 SECTION 1. Chapter 141, Hawaii Revised Statutes, is
2 amended by adding a new section to part IV to be appropriately
3 designated and to read as follows:
4 ”§141- Aquatic livestock import evaluation and
5 authorization process; rules. The division of animal industry
6 may adopt, amend, and repeal rules consistent with applicable
7 law, to develop a science-based evaluation and authorization
8 process to import and transport aquatic livestock within the
9 State. This process shall:
10 (1) Be based on the biological aquatic risk-based
11 framework developed and maintained by the department
12 pursuant to this chapter and chapter 142;
13 (2) Iriclude_niandatory_pre2arrAy^T^_disea^e_testJui22__®IlL£y
