5 risk" has the same meaning as defined in section 141-51, Hawaii
6 Revised Statutes.
7 SECTION 6. Statutory material to be repealed is bracketed
8 and stricken. New statutory material is underscored.
9 SECTION 7. This Act shall take effect on July 1, 2026.
